Jeff Smith spent a year in prison . But what he discovered inside was n’t what he expected -- he saw in his fellow inmates boundless ingenuity and business savvy . He asks : Why do n't we tap this entrepreneurial potential to help ex - prisoners contribute to society once they 're back outside ? 
