And I think they ’re breathing . 
The Nigerian filmmakers really , really , are doing what they like . 
And so it 's a very , very important thing for them , and for their audiences . 
A woman told me , " When I see a Nollywood film , I can relax , I really -- I can breathe better . " 
There is also another very important thing that I hope will resonate with this audience . 
It ’s technology . I ’m very interested in it and I really think that the digital non - linear editing has slashed , you know , the cost now is a fraction of what it used to be . 
Incredible cameras cost under 5,000 dollars . 
